Looks the same.

00:33:31.790 --> 00:33:33.650
Again, those changes that
are occurring on the surface

00:33:33.650 --> 00:33:37.190 position:56%
of the moon are occurring at smaller
scales than what we can see even

00:33:37.190 --> 00:33:39.620
